\f1\fs26 \cf4 \cb3 \strokec4  enables the Rack::Logger middleware which provides a 
\f2\fs23\fsmilli11700 \cf7 \cb8 \strokec7 logger
\f1\fs26 \cf4 \cb3 \strokec4  method in the request context.\cb1 \
