\f1\fs26 \cf4 \cb3 \strokec4  events at all. My validation sync layer should catch this at submit time by reading the current value, but maybe there's a mismatch between what's in the input and what's keyed in my contact map\'97possibly due to whitespace, encoding differences, or how Firefox handles the datalist option values. I'm realizing the simplest fix might be to abandon the hidden field approach entirely and instead validate the contact selection on the server side by looking up the member from the search text. But that requires passing the member ID somehow, which brings me back to the same problem.\cb1 \
