\f2 \cf2 \cb5 \strokec2 ---\
name: script.js cache busting\
description: Must increment ?v=N on script.js URL in both layouts whenever script.js changes\
type: feedback\
---\
\
Bump the version query string on the `script.js` URL in both layout files whenever `script.js` is modified.\
\
Both `app/views/layout.erb` and `app/views/layout_w_logout.erb` reference `/js/script.js?v=N`.\
\
**Why:** Browsers aggressively cache static JS files. If the URL stays the same after a deploy, existing users get stale JS against new HTML \'97 discovered when radio-button validation code was cached while the form had already switched to a hidden field, causing silent validation failures only in browsers that had visited before the deploy.\
\
**How to apply:** Before finishing any task that edits `script.js`, find the current `?v=N` in both layout files and increment N by 1.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

